    • randomMove

      public void randomMove()
      Ant is making random move. It takes random neighbour of current vertex that has not been yet visited and moves to it If there is no such vertex that the ant may go to it returns to its anthill If the Ant is currently on the Stone vertex it also returns to its anthill

    • returnAnthill
